title: Georgia's hyped QB commit already has a Marvel superhero as a fan
text:
Georgia's hyped QB commit already has a Marvel superhero as a fan FOX Sports 
Oct 19, 2015 at 10:28a ET + 
The Jacob Eason hype continues to grow. Daniel Shirey / USA TODAY Sports FOX Sports Updated Oct 19, 2015 at 11:28a ET 
Just how big of a deal is Georgia's five-star quarterback commit Jacob Eason? 247Sports ' No. 1 rated quarterback prospect and No. 2 overall player in the nation is now getting shoutouts from Star-Lord. 
Chris Pratt, the star of Marvel's Guardians of the Galaxy and Jurassic World, is just the latest fan to jump on the Eason bandwagon with this post to his twitter feed, which has nearly three million followers: true #LSHS star QB #JacobEason is nationally ranked for a reason. This kid is damn good. #StraightOuttaLake #GoVikings https://t.co/J4WLpN1wg3 â€” chris pratt (@prattprattpratt) October 18, 2015 
Needless to say, Eason is going to arrive in Athens with a ton of expectations. Can he possibly live up to them all in his first season with the Bulldogs ? true
